Others: Guyana and Martinique are facing off in the CONCACAF Nations League after losing their opening matches.
Guyana's squad for the match has been announced.
The top two finishers from the group will advance to the quarterfinal section in November.
Guyana qualified for League A in the CONCACAF Nations League following a 5-0 record in Group D in League B.
The release stated that after Group Stage play in September and October 2024, the first and second-place finishers of each group will advance to the Quarterfinals.
